&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;      &amp;quot;Core modules initialized. All systems nominal.&amp;quot;&lt;/p&gt;
